front.title: •Insurrection
front.gametext: Deploy on table. Unique (•) Rebels of ability < 3 are forfeit +2. Nabrun Leids and Elis Helrot are limited to owner's move phase and exterior sites. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one docking bay from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: Rebel insurgents and local activists are the first step in breaking the Imperial stranglehold on a world.
